      "type": "exercise",
      "target": "the regional hub. A replacement is now on its way and should arrive by Friday. Please let me know if there's anything else I can help with. Best regards, Lisa.",
      "finger": "purple",
      "hint": "Empathetic email at speed"
    }
  ],
  "character_tips": {
    "anna": "Support is high-volume, real-world typing. Find the even rhythm and the day stops feeling like a sprint.",
